snippet.title: Milo | Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Wishlist 'Milo' on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2665020/Milo/

Music by Craig Amromin

Join the Milo Basketball Challenge and become one of three who will receive a Steam Digital Gift Card. Check the discord for details or visit this link here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2665020/Milo/

'Milo' is a single-player/co-op online multiplayer survival horror game that I am developing for PC. 

Feedback is always welcome. If you have suggestions or ideas, I am always interested in your thoughts. 

Join me on Discord
https://discord.gg/yz8VtVgwq9
